verses.verse: <S%H3051>Give<s%> unto the <S%H3068>Lord<s%>, O you <S%H1121>mighty<s%>, <S%H3051>give<s%> unto the <S%H3068>Lord<s%> <S%H3519>glory<s%> and <S%H5797>strength<s%>.
<S%H3051>Give<s%> unto the <S%H3068>Lord<s%> the <S%H3519>glory<s%> due unto his <S%H8034>name<s%>; <S%H7812>worship<s%> the <S%H3068>Lord<s%> in the <S%H1927>beauty<s%> of <S%H6944>holiness<s%>.

The <S%H6963>voice<s%> of the <S%H3068>Lord<s%> is upon the <S%H4325>waters<s%>: the <S%H410>God<s%> of <S%H3519>glory<s%> <S%H7481>thunders<s%>: the <S%H3068>Lord<s%> is upon <S%H7227>many<s%> <S%H4325>waters<s%>.
The <S%H6963>voice<s%> of the <S%H3068>Lord<s%> is <S%H3581>powerful<s%>; the <S%H6963>voice<s%> of the <S%H3068>Lord<s%> is full of <S%H1926>majesty<s%>.
The <S%H6963>voice<s%> of the <S%H3068>Lord<s%> <S%H7665>breaks<s%> the <S%H730>cedars<s%>; <S%H3068>Yes<s%>, the Lord <S%H7665>breaks<s%> the <S%H730>cedars<s%> of <S%H3844>Lebanon<s%>.
He makes them also to <S%H7540>skip<s%> like a <S%H5695>calf<s%>; <S%H3844>Lebanon<s%> and <S%H8303>Sirion<s%> like a <S%H1121>young<s%> <S%H7214>unicorn<s%>.
The <S%H6963>voice<s%> of the <S%H3068>Lord<s%> <S%H2342>shakes<s%> the <S%H4057>wilderness<s%>; the <S%H3068>Lord<s%> <S%H2342>shakes<s%> the <S%H4057>wilderness<s%> of <S%H6946>Kadesh<s%>.

The <S%H6963>voice<s%> of the <S%H3068>Lord<s%> makes the <S%H355>deer<s%> <S%H2342>calve<s%>, and <S%H2834>discovers<s%> the <S%H3295>forests<s%>: and in his <S%H1964>temple<s%> does every one <S%H559>speak<s%> of his <S%H3519>glory<s%>.
The <S%H3068>Lord<s%> <S%H3427>sits<s%> upon the <S%H3999>flood<s%>; <S%H3068>Yes<s%>, the Lord <S%H3427>sits<s%> <S%H4428>King<s%> for <S%H5769>ever<s%>.
The <S%H3068>Lord<s%> will <S%H5414>give<s%> <S%H5797>strength<s%> unto his <S%H5971>people<s%>; the <S%H3068>Lord<s%> will <S%H1288>bless<s%> his <S%H5971>people<s%> with <S%H7965>peace<s%>.
